        "name": "Jian Yu",
        "email": "yujian@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "yujian"
      },
      "date": "2011-12-26 02:29:47.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\n> Tests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.7/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/3db7b6ce-2d93-11e1-a72c-5254004bbbd3). Ran 13 tests. 1 tests failed: conf-sanity.\n\nconf-sanity test 61 failed because the ldiskfs patch in http://review.whamcloud.com/1708 which supports large xattr has not been landed on master branch yet. The same test passed in http://review.whamcloud.com/1842 which contains the ldiskfs patch.",
